properties.Name: InventoryLocationOnHandBalance

Columns.Description: The quantity of Items on-hand at the Inventory Location.

Columns.Name: ItemQuantityVariance
Columns.Description: The quantity difference between the planned on-hand inventory quantity and the actual on-hand inventory quantity.

Columns.Name: OnHandVarianceReasonId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of the On-Hand Variance Reason.
